## Frequently Asked Questions

**Q: Can I upgrade my license later?**  
A: Yes, you can upgrade at any time. We'll prorate your existing license credit.

**Q: What happens if I cancel?**  
A: You can use the software until the end of your billing period. Tours created remain usable forever.

**Q: Do I get all future versions?**  
A: Your license includes all minor updates (5.3.x → 5.4.x). Major versions (5.x → 6.x) are available at 50% discount.

**Q: Can I install on multiple computers?**  
A: Yes, within your user seat limit. Enterprise licenses allow unlimited installations.

**Q: What if I exceed my user seat limit?**  
A: Contact us to add seats. Additional seats are prorated for the remainder of your license term.

**Q: Do you offer refunds?**  
A: 30-day money-back guarantee if the software doesn't meet your needs.

**Q: Can I get a demo before purchasing?**  
A: Yes, we offer a 14-day trial for brokerages. Contact sales.

